Don't try to open an already opened tempfile when compressing uploads.
Add CHANGELOG.rst to the repo to track changes easier.

Don't try to open an already opened tempfile when compressing uploads.

On Windows, trying to open() the writable tempfile leads to a permissions error.
Instead just open the file once and seek() to the start of the file when we are
done writing to it.
